1
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,600
Zheng Minjiang!

2
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:44,880
I finally caught you, didn't I?

3
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:48,520
Li Guangming.

4
00:00:49,439 --> 00:00:50,320
What are you doing here?

5
00:00:51,359 --> 00:00:52,399
I knew it.

6
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,479
You were up to no good.

7
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,479
I didn't expect you to violate factory rules

8
00:00:56,719 --> 00:00:58,520
by moonlighting here for someone else.

9
00:00:59,439 --> 00:01:00,799
I'm off the clock.

10
00:01:01,039 --> 00:01:01,880
I'm helping a friend.

11
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,880
It's not moonlighting.

12
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,599
You're a technician at a state-owned factory.

13
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:06,760
I caught you moonlighting,

14
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,159
and you still dare to make excuses?

15
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,120
Let me ask you then.

16
00:01:09,239 --> 00:01:09,680
This...

17
00:01:09,879 --> 00:01:10,519
vinegar workshop...

18
00:01:10,760 --> 00:01:11,879
which "friend" does it belong to?

19
00:01:12,079 --> 00:01:13,159
What's it to you?

20
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:15,560
I'm your superior.

21
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:17,920
You violated factory regulations,

22
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,079
and you still dare to talk back?

23
00:01:20,799 --> 00:01:21,079
This...

24
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:22,000
this toolbox...

25
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,159
does it belong to the factory?

26
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:26,200
You're actually wrong about that.

27
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:27,599
These tools...

28
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,280
were a gift from my mentor.

29
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:31,519
Today, I'm definitely

30
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:33,239
going to get something on you.

31
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,519
Wang Yingrong.

32
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:39,319
Li Guangming.

33
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,519
What are you doing here?

34
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,040
Li Guangming,

35
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:44,840
don't go looking for trouble.

36
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,319
I helped her without taking a cent.

37
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,560
It's not moonlighting.

38
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:48,879
No matter who asks,

39
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,079
I'll say the same thing.

40
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:52,040
So she's the "friend" you mentioned?

41
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:55,760
Wang Yingrong is the factory's famous slut.

42
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,200
Is that how desperate you are?

43
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,000
I'm going to kill you!

44
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,000
Watch your mouth!

45
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,519
Yingrong's reputation...

46
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,200
It's bad apples like you

47
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,879
who ruined it!

48
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,759
Still protecting your little mistress?

49
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,719
And you claim you two are clean?

50
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,120
I think the two of you are just...

51
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:15,960
Say one more word!

52
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:18,000
I'll make you regret coming here today!

53
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,159
What are you doing?

54
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:21,240
You want to hit me, huh?

55
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,319
Let me tell you,

56
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,280
a wise man knows when to retreat.

57
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:26,280
Just you wait!

58
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:28,560
Just wait!

59
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:30,800
Coward.

60
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:35,199
It's okay now.

61
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:35,919
I'm leaving.

62
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,280
Stand there.

63
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:52,919
Mom.

64
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,120
You're still up?

65
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,000
Do you have any money left?

66
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,439
Let me tell you.

67
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,039
Yingtang needs money this time...

68
00:03:01,199 --> 00:03:02,479
...for something important.

69
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,080
She needs to pay her tuition fees.

70
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:06,360
If it's late, the teacher won't take it.

71
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,879
Give me another fifty.

72
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,319
Mom.

73
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,439
Are you really this biased?

74
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,840
I don't even have a job now.

75
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,120
The pigs are gone too.

76
00:03:15,199 --> 00:03:16,599
And I can't catch many fish either.

77
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:17,240
Mom.

78
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,759
Look at me.

79
00:03:18,879 --> 00:03:20,039
I'm having a hard time too.

80
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,719
You brought it on yourself.

81
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,360
Is your sister anything like you?

82
00:03:23,599 --> 00:03:25,360
She's about to be a college student.

83
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:26,360
By the way.

84
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,560
Where's that motorcycle of yours?

85
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:28,840
Go sell it.

86
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,080
And give the money to your sister.

87
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:35,159
I raised you through shit and piss.

88
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,080
Not only do you not earn money for us...

89
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,199
...but you act like...

90
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,879
...we owe you something.

91
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,120
You Plague.

92
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,599
Here they come.

93
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,000
I've been saving this table for you.

94
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:50,639
Please, come inside.

95
00:03:50,639 --> 00:03:50,960
Great.

96
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:52,159
Come on.

97
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:52,759
Young Boss Tang.

98
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:53,479
Please, come inside.

99
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:56,599
Young Boss Tang.

100
00:03:59,080 --> 00:04:00,000
Brother-in-law.

101
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:02,759
Yingtang.

102
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,319
What are you two doing...

103
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,159
This is my boyfriend.

104
00:04:08,599 --> 00:04:09,520
Tang Yan.

105
00:04:19,279 --> 00:04:20,040
Young Boss Tang.

106
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:22,759
Yingtang.

107
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:24,040
Why are you just standing there?

108
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:25,120
Pour the drinks.

109
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:27,399
Okay.

110
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:37,120
Director Li.

111
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,800
The machines in our factory...

112
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,800
...you fixed them.

113
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,600
I really appreciate it.

114
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,600
Just doing my job.

115
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,199
Yingtang.

116
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,879
We're celebrating today.

117
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,839
Have a drink.

118
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:53,519
I don't drink.

119
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,199
It's no big deal.

120
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,319
This is grain alcohol.

121
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,600
It's smooth and won't go to your head.

122
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:01,600
Don't worry.

123
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,959
Young Boss Tang is impressive.

124
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,560
My dad's factory has so much business...

125
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,879
...and lots of social events.

126
00:05:23,279 --> 00:05:24,480
If you can't drink...

127
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:26,680
...how can I take you out in the future?

128
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,480
Pour it up.

129
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,680
Then I'll try a little.

130
00:05:37,879 --> 00:05:39,199
Fill it up.

131
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,360
That's about enough.

132
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:51,000
Brother-in-law will have a drink with you.

133
00:05:52,959 --> 00:05:53,680
Bottoms up.

134
00:05:55,279 --> 00:05:56,199
Director Li.

135
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,160
Not bad.

136
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:09,800
Uncle Fang.

137
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,199
The vinegar is ready.

138
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,040
The vinegar is ready.

139
00:06:13,519 --> 00:06:14,040
Come, come.

140
00:06:14,279 --> 00:06:14,759
Put it here.

141
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:15,839
Careful, careful.

142
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,639
Come, take a look.

143
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,279
How is it, Uncle Fang?

144
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:40,759
Yingrong.

145
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:42,279
I knew I was right about you.

146
00:06:42,759 --> 00:06:43,360
This batch of vinegar...

147
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,079
I'll take it all.

148
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:44,800
It's a deal.

149
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,399
That's great, Uncle Fang.

150
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:47,360
If my driver hadn't

151
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,120
gone back to his hometown,

152
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,160
I'd go over to your place to get the vinegar right now.

153
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:51,959
It's no problem.

154
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,240
If you have a truck, lend it to me.

155
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,160
I'll transport it to you.

156
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:55,600
You know how to drive?

157
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,519
I don't.

158
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,519
But someone does.

159
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:58,920
Zheng Minjiang!

160
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:00,639
Come here, quick.

161
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:02,800
Hello, Uncle Fang.

162
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,879
Are you two...

163
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,759
He owes me a debt right now.

164
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:13,360
He's working for me to pay it off.

165
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:15,720
I see.

166
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:17,959
Good, good. Here.

167
00:07:18,279 --> 00:07:18,680
Take this.

168
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:19,519
I'm leaving now.

169
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,519
I really am getting old.

170
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,519
Thinking about how young people date these days...

171
00:07:24,519 --> 00:07:25,519
it's all so novel.

172
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,279
Thanks for fixing the machine for me this time.

173
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,519
I've decided.

174
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:30,480
From now on, I...

175
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,079
Wang Yingtang!

176
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:39,600
Sis?

177
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:42,800
What are you doing?

178
00:07:43,199 --> 00:07:45,360
Sis, why are you here?

179
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,240
I should be asking you that.

180
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,199
You're not at school.

181
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,480
What are you doing here?

182
00:07:49,439 --> 00:07:50,040
Hey!

183
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,480
Who are you people?

184
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:53,720
Wang Yingrong.

185
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,399
I wanted to talk to you last time.

186
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:57,360
A grown girl like you...

187
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,360
hanging around every day with that

188
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,839
shady man.

189
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,040
what are you trying to do?

190
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,759
What did you say?

191
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,399
That's none of your business.

192
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,480
Come back with me.

193
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:10,279
I'm out eating with classmates.

194
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:11,639
Leave me alone.

195
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:13,360
Aren't you supposed to be in remedial class?

196
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:14,839
So what?

197
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,040
Remedial drinking class?

198
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:17,439
Wang Yingtang!

199
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:19,720
You're too young to be drinking.

200
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,560
Would decent friends make you drink?

201
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:22,879
Can't you see those people

202
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:23,920
have ulterior motives?

203
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:24,879
Come back with me.

204
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:29,480
Wang Yingrong.

205
00:08:30,079 --> 00:08:31,959
Yingtang came here

206
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,440
to learn how to socialize.

207
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:37,159
With me, her brother-in-law, watching over her...

208
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,120
what are you worried about?

209
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,879
Li Guangming!

210
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,559
You are rotten to the core.

211
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:44,159
Wang Yingtang is your sister-in-law.

212
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,279
You're helping outsiders

213
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:46,600
to get her drunk.

214
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:48,279
Don't think I don't know what you're up to.

215
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,480
Where did this guy pop out from?

216
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,840
Such a busybody.

217
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:55,480
Young Boss Tang.

218
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:58,039
This is the one I just told you about.

219
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,480
That little employee from our factory.

220
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:04,200
So he's just a hired hand.

221
00:09:04,480 --> 00:09:05,519
I can't be bothered with your nonsense.

222
00:09:05,679 --> 00:09:06,279
Come with me.

223
00:09:06,879 --> 00:09:07,480
Hey!

224
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,840
You think you can come and go as you please?

225
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:12,279
Where does that leave my reputation?

226
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:13,919
What do you mean?

227
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:15,639
What do I mean?

228
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,039
I was happy today.

229
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:19,360
For Yingtang...

230
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,399
I opened bottles worth hundreds of yuan.

231
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:22,919
If you want to take her away, fine.

232
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:24,679
Finish the wine.

233
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,679
There's a whole bottle left here.

234
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,720
If I drink it all...

235
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,039
I'd have to be carried out.

236
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:33,320
You don't have to drink it.

237
00:09:34,399 --> 00:09:35,480
Then don't take her away.

238
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,120
You...

239
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,919
What kind of man forces a woman to drink?

240
00:09:38,799 --> 00:09:39,639
I'll drink it for her.

241
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,559
It's okay.

242
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:13,720
Let's go.

243
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:15,559
Move.

244
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:19,639
Hey.

245
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:20,960
I told her to drink.

246
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,840
I didn't tell you to drink.

247
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:24,480
Your drinking doesn't count.

248
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:26,799
Exactly.

249
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:28,879
Young Boss Tang told her to drink.

250
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,159
That's giving her face.

251
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:30,960
It's not...

252
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,120
your place as an outsider to speak.

253
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:35,039
Don't go too far.

254
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:36,039
Stop pretending.

255
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,720
You two...

256
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:39,519
might have even slept together.

257
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,360
Young Boss Tang.

258
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,919
This is what I told you about.

259
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:46,960
The factory's famous slut.

260
00:10:49,799 --> 00:10:50,879
What a piece of trash.

261
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:51,799
Zheng Minjiang.

262
00:10:51,799 --> 00:10:52,840
Stop hitting him!

263
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:53,799
Don't hit him!

264
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,879
Stop fighting!

265
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:09,879
You're finally awake.

266
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,480
Why am I in the hospital?

267
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:19,000
Didn't I beat up Li Guangming?

268
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,799
You're really something.

269
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,759
Why try to be a hero?

270
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:24,559
You drank yourself unconscious.

271
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,840
Drinking when you can't handle it.

272
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,960
I really can't hold my liquor well.

273
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,399
Wang Yingrong.

274
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,360
What happened to my head?

275
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:43,200
You drank too much.

276
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:47,279
Zheng Minjiang.

277
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,159
Oh my god.

278
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:01,399
Zheng Minjiang.

279
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,519
Zheng Minjiang.

280
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:06,879
It's over. That's a huge bump.

281
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,080
I just accidentally pushed you a little.

282
00:12:13,279 --> 00:12:14,360
As luck would have it...

283
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:16,279
you hit the doorframe.

284
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,720
But the doctor checked it.

285
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,960
It's fine.

286
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:21,840
Really.

287
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,480
Why do I feel like...

288
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,159
you did it on purpose?

289
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,759
Am I, Wang Yingrong, that kind of person?

290
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,360
What kind of person?

291
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,360
Why are you here?

292
00:12:36,919 --> 00:12:37,919
I called him over to take care of you.

293
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:38,919
I'm going back. Take this.

294
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,200
Why are you leaving?

295
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:53,399
You pretended so well.

296
00:12:53,399 --> 00:12:54,440
She's already gone far.

297
00:12:58,919 --> 00:13:00,039
It hurts, bro.

298
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,159
Bro.

299
00:13:05,279 --> 00:13:06,279
For Sister Yingrong...

300
00:13:06,919 --> 00:13:08,279
you almost risked your life.

301
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:10,120
That was awesome.

302
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,600
Is this move of yours called...

303
00:13:12,919 --> 00:13:14,600
A fit of rage for a beauty?

304
00:13:17,399 --> 00:13:18,120
This is called...

305
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:20,080
endless debts to a creditor.

306
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,240
Who doesn't know that you... towards Sister Yingrong...

307
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,440
Get lost.

308
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:51,960
Zheng Minjiang.

309
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:54,240
You are simply lawless.

310
00:13:54,399 --> 00:13:55,279
Look at what you did to your leader.

311
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,960
Look how badly you beat him up.

312
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,080
Li Guangming has a foul mouth.

313
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:02,519
I think he deserved to be taught a lesson.

314
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:03,159
You...

315
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:04,919
Alright, Zheng Minjiang.

316
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,759
Moonlighting, hitting a leader.

317
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,399
And you still dare to talk back to me?

318
00:14:09,039 --> 00:14:09,639
Zheng Minjiang.

319
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,279
If you... this time...

320
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,600
kneel down right now...

321
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:13,600
and kowtow once loudly...

322
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,840
I might let you off this time.

323
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,440
I, Zheng Minjiang, kneel to heaven, earth, and my parents.

324
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,519
Why should I kneel to someone like you?

325
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:23,759
Director Wu.

326
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:24,480
Look at this.

327
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,080
Look.

328
00:14:25,559 --> 00:14:26,159
Zheng Minjiang.

329
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,120
Kneel down right now.

330
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,360
Apologize to Guangming.

331
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,039
Otherwise...

332
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:32,919
I will demote you right now.

333
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,480
Go to the workshop and carry cement.

334
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,320
I'm a Grade 8 technician.

335
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,519
I didn't violate factory regulations.

336
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,000
On what grounds are you demoting me?

337
00:14:41,279 --> 00:14:43,240
Because you offended leadership and disobeyed.

338
00:14:45,039 --> 00:14:46,320
Say whatever you want.

339
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,200
I don't want to waste words with people like you.

340
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,240
You're so arrogant.

341
00:14:53,679 --> 00:14:54,519
What are you doing?
